      <title>The race is so close. Here's what happens if there's a 269-269 Electoral College tie</title>
      <author>Ashley Lopez</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/10/21/nx-s1-5150099/electoral-college-tie-explainer</link>
      <comments>https://text.npr.org/2024/10/21/nx-s1-5150099/electoral-college-tie-explainer</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.npr.org/2024/10/21/nx-s1-5150099/electoral-college-tie-explainer</guid>
